Package: rsegregation
Type: Package
Title: Calculate Empirical Measures of Segregation
Version: 0.0.1
Author: Arthur Gailes
Maintainer: Arthur Gailes <arthurgailes@berkeley.edu>
Description: Provides functions for several empirical measures of racial segregation.
    Includes divergence, entropy, dissimilarity, exposure, isolation, and location quotient.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
